i.imgur.com/XpLhiiZ.jpg\"></p>\n<p>The Over warning appears when you have completely ran out of data or exceeded it. Again it immediately turns off mobile data and gives you the option to visit your mobile provider (via WiFi) to purchase data.</p>\n<h3>Automation Setup</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"Setup Automation \" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqxcKsh.jpg\">\n1. Open Shortcuts open 'Automation' at the bottom and of the app.\n2. Select the + symbol at the top right corner.\n3. Select 'Personal Automation'.\n4. Select \"Time of Day'.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Setup automation \" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8t18ZRj.jpg\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Enter the time you wish the automation to run in 'Time of Day'.</li>\n<li>Select 'Daily' then click 'Next' in the top right corner.</li>\n<li>Click 'Add Action and search 'Run Shortcut\".</li>\n<li>Tap on the word 'Shortcut' next to 'Run' and Search 'DataMan Automation'.</li>\n<li>Click 'Next in the top right hand corner and toggle the 'Ask Before Running' off - on the Warning pop up that follows click 'Don't Ask'.</li>\n<li>Click 'Done' in the top right corner.</li>\n</ol>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.8 - June 29, 2021, 12:43 a.m.</strong></p><p>- Improved data statistics presentation with HTML splash screen.<br>- Improved monthly start summary with HTML splash screen<br><br>Like this Shortcut? Please Heart us on the shortcut page!!<br>Thanks</p>"}